			IMX952_PAD_SD1_DATA5__WAKEUPMIX_TOP_USDHC1_DATA5	0x13fe
			IMX952_PAD_SD1_DATA6__WAKEUPMIX_TOP_USDHC1_DATA6	0x13fe
